    <string name="help_how_to_play">How to play the game</string>
    <string name="help_game_intro">The upper grid displays the game field of your opponent, the lower grid displays your own game field. To play the game, proceed as follows.</string>
    <string name="help_dialog_title">How to play</string>
    <string name="help_game_step_one">1. Choose a cell you want to attack by clicking on it.</string>
    <string name="help_game_step_two">2. Press the \"FIRE\" button to confirm. The cell becomes red to indicate a hit, or blue to indicate a miss.</string>
    <string name="help_game_step_three">3. In case of a hit, you can attack your opponents grid again.</string>
    <string name="help_game_step_four">4. In case of a miss, click the \"DONE\" button to end your turn and hand the phone to your opponent, who may attack your ships. If you play against the computer, the computer will attack your ships.</string>
